    "title": "צֹנֶה אֵילִים כְּבָשִׂים וּרְחֵלִים | Tsoneh Eilim Kvasim uRḥelim — an ofan piyyut for Rosh haShanah la-Behemah by Isaac Gantwerk Mayer",
